{"tid":1358031,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發] 林鄭的終極陰謀","createTime":"2019-07-24T00:27:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-24T00:34:27.000Z","uid":261211,"like":4,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"bccaa50f58d752aff3219d017637ac66e4328e7f","tid":1358031,"uid":261211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T00:27:52.000Z","msg":"有朋友係有勢力人士，收到風林鄭<span style=\"color: red;\">想借今次整頓丁權同僭建</span>。<br />\n大家都知林鄭仲係政務司時已經想搞班鄉紳，但坐上後基於形勢，而且鄉紳有中共人脈，只能暫時閣置，但一直深深不忿。<br />\n今次係想借示威者嘅手搞亂元朗勢力，又可以岀師有名拘捕示威者，一石二鳥借力打力。<br />\n<br />\n究竟邊個軍師咁勁諗到呢條妙計？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2303b602ec8464d769b8a442cc97ff88dfb4c7d8","tid":1358031,"uid":192971,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T00:28:15.000Z","msg":"連登仔明白未? 要完全脫離共產黨先會有出路?<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1351752\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1351752</a><br />\n<br />\n不要說「推」，試著說「光復革命 香港獨立」<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1356481\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1356481</a><br />\n<br />\n光復革命 香港獨立 ！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30c474c47d28c316958ac19b4102cbe38b9bfc9b","tid":1358031,"uid":4942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T00:28:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n陰謀論夠未"},{"pid":"a1ead8a781e3fa36ae6237563ae9cf0134fb9fda","tid":1358031,"uid":139256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T00:29:23.000Z","msg":"香港人無陰謀得訴求，理撚得佢咩陰謀"},{"pid":"4f28225a105f244817ac6efcfb904514d6648942","tid":1358031,"uid":262053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T00:29:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/34.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"841e5c5db30441343d85d92e9ab8b5d0208daf73","tid":1358031,"uid":88428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T00:31:10.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我有朋友係外星人添</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">五毛警報極高<br />\n五毛升級分化<br />\n頭腦必須清醒</span></span><br />\n<br />\n726 機場 - [突發] 7月26 香港國際機場集會<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1354319\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1354319</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n727 元朗 （重點）- 元朗遊行已遞交不反對通知書<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1355504\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1355504</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n728 上環 （新增）-【毋忘上環】7.28上環追究開槍大遊行<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1356713\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1356713</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n84 將軍澳 - 【正式宣布】8月4日 舉行 「將軍澳反送中大遊行」<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1356143\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1356143</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"5c3b2b8148514098bcdc521f3c3e6a2ac321ab0e","tid":1358031,"uid":276150,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T00:31:35.000Z","msg":"我都睇好多陰謀論，但我最重視係實際行動，陰謀論或者中計論係令人乜都唔好做嘅最佳藉口。其實你諗深一層麥當勞嘅存在都係一個陰謀嚟㗎，咁你又去買黎食？？咁你咪中咗麥當勞計囉？"},{"pid":"92965c794a6028d046dc4abec0ba788d4c2aba88","tid":1358031,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T00:34:27.000Z","msg":"樓主 = 林鄭條陰毛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}